comprehensive care to women.

00:42:26.020 --> 00:42:30.820
We feel we need to serve the
needs of women, all of them

00:42:30.820 --> 00:42:34.330
with no exceptions when it
comes to reproductive and sexual

00:42:34.330 --> 00:42:35.220
care.

00:42:35.220 --> 00:42:38.480
And that's how we stand
as an organization,

00:42:38.480 --> 00:42:42.470
and that can be easily
verified by our annual report.

00:42:42.470 --> 00:42:44.774
It hasn't changed much
